IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EDITDEMO.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 AMT    PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 1234.56.
01 PRETTY PIC ZZ,ZZ9.99.
01 GRADE  PIC 9 VALUE 2.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE AMT TO PRETTY.
    DISPLAY "Amount: " PRETTY.
    EVALUATE GRADE
       WHEN 1 DISPLAY "grade one"
       WHEN 2 DISPLAY "grade two"
       WHEN OTHER DISPLAY "other grade"
    END-EVALUATE.
    STOP RUN.
